Lucy Speed https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucy_Speed 0 Lucy Renee Speed (born 31 August 1976) is an English actress best known for her television roles as Natalie Evans (née Price) in the BBC One soap opera EastEnders, and as DS Stevie Moss in the ITV1 police drama series The Bill.
